para_trans: Regarding sanction of Primary Health Centre at Mauje Malegaon (Makta), Taluka Deglur, District Nanded.
Government Decision No: Grade - 2024 / Q. No.281 / Health-4
Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, Mumbai: J. No. AASE / Room-7A / T-5 / Malegaon Makta / ProAKE / Manzoor / Nanded / 2962-64/2024, D. Letter of 07.08.2023.
Introduction: - To the citizens of Mauje Malegaon (Makta), Taluka Deglur, District Nanded
Since it is necessary to sanction a new primary health centre in line with the provision of health facilities.
The issue of sanctioning a primary health centre at the site was under consideration of the government. In this regard, the following
Government Decision: - New Primary as a "Special Matter" at Mauje Malegaon (Makta), Taluka Deglur, District Nanded
Approval is being given to sanction a health centre.
2. Acquisition of space for this Primary Health Centre in the prescribed manner at the site of the Primary Health Centre.
Separate action on construction of health centre, post creation from district planning fund
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
